&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204820151/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2833/33204820151_ba750feec3_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170303_184200&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;saturday-taipei-and-tamsui&#34;&gt;Saturday - Taipei and Tamsui&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The last day was spent with a walk in the park - botanical garden of Taipei, some coffee drinking and lunch eating where we were joined again by CJ.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/32489972714/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3900/32489972714_ee412d8d1a_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_103818&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204820521/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3837/33204820521_6424b18040_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_110013&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/32489973064/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3934/32489973064_ec6a137211_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_122647&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204820711/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2833/33204820711_66952b4f2b_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_122713&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And then we had a trip to Tamsui 淡水, where we did most sightseeing places, like the Red Fortress, the White House, the Mackay church, Alethia University with the Oxford building (made with &lt;em&gt;real red bricks&lt;/em&gt;!!!), though not Tamsui high school, which after an incident last year apparently is kind of closed off for the public.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204821001/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3750/33204821001_6eeffd4ba3_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_151813&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/32489973874/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2866/32489973874_3287fab95d_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_151942&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204821441/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/624/33204821441_67ca376afc_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_152044_HDR&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33177394072/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3700/33177394072_0d90f82572_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;IMG_20170304_154935&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/32949978430/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2899/32949978430_ef7cb41680_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_155129&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33332660605/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3864/33332660605_bd938541e4_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;IMG_20170304_155712&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/32949978570/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/635/32949978570_7e9fa8f574_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_162132_HDR&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33204821711/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3684/33204821711_17e4c6d179_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;20170304_162125&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After some Korean barbecue it was time to send them home - I had a really nice time with my friends. &lt;em&gt;Tien op tien.&lt;/em&gt; I gave them a farewell huggy and a farewell Chunky, a Kitkat bar which &lt;em&gt;obviously&lt;/em&gt; has been named after Chunky Kaishek, before I put them on the bus to the airport. Thank you. Come again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/33177394182/in/album-72157677792518233/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/3/2873/33177394182_87b0caee5d_b.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;IMG_20170304_195257&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
