&lt;p&gt;A long overdue update, but my friends have implored me to write it down. In the last update I talked about the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.thomasvanhoey.com/blog/artsy-fartsy-afternoons&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Artsy Fartsy Afternoon&lt;/a&gt; I had after my &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.thomasvanhoey.com/blog/visit-from-vietnam&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Visit from Vietnam&lt;/a&gt;. Today my treat for you is a Visit from Japan and how I spent Chinese New Year 2016.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;under-the-bamboo&#34;&gt;Under the Bamboo&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Last year, my dear Japanese friend Takeshita 竹下 &amp;ldquo;Under the bamboo&amp;rdquo; came to visit me and Joke in Belgium and we had a wonderful time. She had been a classmate of us in Suzhou. This is my favourite picture I have of her, entitled &amp;ldquo;Takeshita under the bamboo&amp;rdquo; 竹下の竹下.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/26447794645/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1573/26447794645_519b7b5dd0_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;竹下の竹下&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At the end of January she came for a weekend to Taipei, all the way from Japan. She had so much luggage with her — a whole handbag. She told me that the flight attendants were perplexed, and so was I. However, I think it was magical, like Harry Potter, for she seemed to be able to find everything she needed at a whim, and we all know that is not a given with the vast oceans that women&amp;rsquo;s purses often are.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We first went to the Confucius temple (note: I have written about these temples and spots before, so just read more posts on my blog if you want to know more about them), where we did the customary jumping picture.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/25162391175/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1564/25162391175_09bd19f9e9_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Takeshita jumping with Confucius&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Afterwards, we saw how clean they kept the Bao&amp;rsquo;an temple, by using a toothbrush. I wonder which toothpaste they use to clean though.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/24535555283/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1720/24535555283_6efb8fd10f_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Brushing those stelae&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Later we went to Jiufen, but it was raining and misty, so it wasn&amp;rsquo;t that much fun. However, I think she had some fun because she got to see the teahouse from the award winning anime movie &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spirited_Away&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Spirited Away&lt;/a&gt;. Here is the teahouse with Takeshita:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/24531710354/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1627/24531710354_b1a773c2e5_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;2016-01-30 18.05.49&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The next day, the weather gods were nicer to us. We went to see Chiang Kai-Shek&amp;rsquo;s and Sun Yat-sen&amp;rsquo;s memorial halls, saw Taipei 101 – the big tower –, had lunch in &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Din_Tai_Fung&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Din Tai Fung&lt;/a&gt; and went inside the City Hall. Here&amp;rsquo;s pics:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/25162392395/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1596/25162392395_c2bb51ddf9_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;2016-01-31 11.00.27&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/24531711004/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1501/24531711004_7afbbaeabe_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;2016-01-31 12.57.21&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/86097314@N03/24535557103/in/album-72157664759205081/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1716/24535557103_21ea5c383a_z.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;2016-01-31 12.57.28&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

